COLOR SCHEME: Blue-White Professional Theme
===============================================

PRIMARY COLORS:
- Dark backgrounds: slate-950/slate-900 → white/gray-50
- Primary accent: red-600/red-500 → blue-600/blue-500  
- Secondary accent: red-400 → blue-600
- Light accent: red-300 → blue-500

BORDER COLORS:
- border-red-500/* → border-blue-300/border-blue-400
- border-red-400/* → border-blue-200/border-blue-300

BACKGROUND COLORS:
- bg-red-950/* → bg-blue-50/bg-blue-100
- bg-red-600/* → bg-blue-600
- from-red-950 → from-blue-100
- to-red-950 → to-white/to-gray-50

TEXT COLORS:
- text-white → text-gray-900
- text-gray-300/gray-200 → text-gray-700/gray-600
- text-red-300/red-400 → text-blue-600
- text-gray-400 → text-gray-500

SHADOW COLORS:
- shadow-red-600/* → shadow-blue-300/*

